# Build

```bash
g++ -std=c++23 main.cpp -lsqlite3 -o engine.exe
```

---

# Run

```bash
./engine.exe
```

Windows

```powershell
.\engine.exe
```

---

# Launch Dashboard

```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

---

# Recovery

```bash
./engine.exe --recover
```

